  "detailed_description": "<strong>Note: This game is made entirely by a single person and may have many shortcomings,bugs,etc. Thank you very much for the understanding and patience .</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155710/extras/8b3c6e4169ca6a43f730c1ce76d8ea77.poster.avif?t=1727860182\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155710/extras/8b3c6e4169ca6a43f730c1ce76d8ea77.webm?t=1727860182\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155710/extras/8b3c6e4169ca6a43f730c1ce76d8ea77.mp4?t=1727860182\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The game is a story-driven RPG that uses turn-based battle system.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155710/extras/d80b57de43a4ab674a855c9d52490a62.poster.avif?t=1727860182\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155710/extras/d80b57de43a4ab674a855c9d52490a62.webm?t=1727860182\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155710/extras/d80b57de43a4ab674a855c9d52490a62.mp4?t=1727860182\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong> You will lead a bounty team on a special adventure in a cyberpunk-like sci-fi world. </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155710/extras/0941c4b3ddd390268509948ae92da79f.poster.avif?t=1727860182\" width=638 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155710/extras/0941c4b3ddd390268509948ae92da79f.webm?t=1727860182\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155710/extras/0941c4b3ddd390268509948ae92da79f.mp4?t=1727860182\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong> A cyberpunk-like adventure world using pixel style<br>The battle system that integrates dynamic weather system, skills, striker system, stunts, traits and other content makes the battle full of fun and strategy</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155710/extras/640c35ca9687ece2fe39ff2a78174595.poster.avif?t=1727860182\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155710/extras/640c35ca9687ece2fe39ff2a78174595.webm?t=1727860182\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155710/extras/640c35ca9687ece2fe39ff2a78174595.mp4?t=1727860182\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong> Various equipment, items, cybernetics, tattoos, and other elements are used to enhance the various attributes of characters.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155710/extras/98faf020daec64cc4bb0bf0af011d1da.poster.avif?t=1727860182\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155710/extras/98faf020daec64cc4bb0bf0af011d1da.webm?t=1727860182\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155710/extras/98faf020daec64cc4bb0bf0af011d1da.mp4?t=1727860182\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>In addition to the main storyline, the game also includes various side quests and random events. There are multiple mini-games, gashapon collections, and other elements that allow players to unlock new features or obtain new rewards.</strong>",
